    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a Double VANOS variable valve timing system, both recently serviced to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain consists of a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a cooling system overhaul with a high-capacity radiator. The suspension geometry is enhanced by Bilstein dampers, providing precise turn-in and controlled damping cycles. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the powertrain and chassis remains rigid and responsive, making it an ideal candidate for spirited driving or club events.",
